[CEO TOUR ALERT]: 👉 Check out the full episode. Link in bio! 

One of the longest-independent-running gyms in downtown Mississauga, Ontario, Habitual Fitness & Lifestyle stands out with an education and habit development approach to fitness goals. 

Watch as WellnessLiving CEO & Co-Founder, Len Fridman chats with @habitual_fitness owner/co-founder @habitual.adam to learn more about this ego-free gym and their range of health services, including physiotherapy and osteopathy to help members overcome injuries and handle setbacks. 

Then, see how switching to WellnessLiving in 2019 helped them simplify operations and drive member retention.
